  "local_port": 44298,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What is the best and most economic perfume for men in India?",
  "response": "Choosing the right fragrance can enhance your personal style and leave a lasting impression. In India, there are several high-quality yet economical perfumes for men that offer great value without compromising on scent or longevity. Below are some of the best and most budget-friendly options available:\n\n### 1. **Engage Homme**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9300 - \u20b9500\n- **Notes:** Fresh, fruity, and woody notes make this fragrance versatile for daily wear.\n- **Why It\u2019s Popular:** Provides a pleasant scent that lasts long, making it a favorite among young professionals.\n\n### 2. **Park Avenue Intense**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9500 - \u20b9700\n- **Notes:** Combines spicy and woody elements with a hint of sweetness.\n- **Why It\u2019s Popular:** Known for its sophisticated aroma suitable for both office and evening occasions.\n\n### 3. **Fogg Scent for Men**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9200 - \u20b9400\n- **Notes:** Citrus, floral, and woody notes blend to create a refreshing fragrance.\n- **Why It\u2019s Popular:** Highly affordable with good longevity, making it ideal for everyday use.\n\n### 4. **Wild Stone Code**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9300 - \u20b9500\n- **Notes:** Earthy and woody notes with a hint of spice.\n- **Why It\u2019s Popular:** Offers a strong and masculine scent that\u2019s perfect for casual and formal settings.\n\n### 5. **Ustraa Deodorant Spray (Fragranced)**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9200 - \u20b9400\n- **Notes:** Crisp and invigorating with subtle musk undertones.\n- **Why It\u2019s Popular:** Combines deodorant with a light fragrance, offering convenience and affordability.\n\n### 6. **Denver Hamilton**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9400 - \u20b9600\n- **Notes:** Fresh citrus blended with woody and spicy accords.\n- **Why It\u2019s Popular:** Long-lasting scent with a balanced composition suitable for all seasons.\n\n### 7. **Dosar Men Perfume**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9250 - \u20b9450\n- **Notes:** A mix of fresh spicy and woody notes.\n- **Why It\u2019s Popular:** Excellent value for money with a classy scent profile.\n\n### 8. **Nautica Voyage**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b91,200 - \u20b92,000 (often available at discounted rates)\n- **Notes:** Fresh aquatic notes combined with green leaves and a hint of apple.\n- **Why It\u2019s Popular:** Offers a high-end fragrance experience at a relatively affordable price point when on sale.\n\n### Tips for Choosing an Economical Perfume:\n1. **Understand Your Preferences:** Know whether you prefer fresh, woody, spicy, or oriental scents.\n2. **Check Longevity:** Look for perfumes that offer longer-lasting scents to get better value.\n3. **Read Reviews:** Customer reviews can provide insights into the fragrance\u2019s performance and scent profile.\n4. **Sample First:** If possible, try a sample before purchasing to ensure it suits your taste.\n5. **Consider Concentration:** Eau de Toilette generally offers a good balance between scent intensity and price.\n\n### Where to Buy:\n- **Online Retailers:** Amazon India, Flipkart, Nykaa, and other e-commerce platforms often have competitive prices and discounts.\n- **Local Stores:** Visiting local perfume shops or department stores can allow you to test fragrances before buying.\n- **Off-Season Sales:** Keep an eye out for festive sales and clearance offers to grab your favorite scents at lower prices.\n\n### Conclusion\nThere are numerous economical yet high-quality perfumes available for men in India. Brands like Engage, Park Avenue, Fogg, and Wild Stone consistently offer fragrances that balance affordability with appealing scents and good longevity. By considering your personal preferences and taking advantage of sales or discounts, you can find the perfect fragrance that fits both your style and budget.",
